title: (RESERVED)
content:
For property used or developed as a special use described in Section 25-2-1403, (Special Uses):

(1)

the regulations prescribed by this subchapter supersede the other provisions of Title 25 (Land Development) to the extent of conflict; and

(2)

the following regulations do not apply:

(a)

Section 25-2-514 (Open Space Standards);

(b)

Section 25-2-775 (Townhouses); and

(c)

Section 25-2-776 (Condominium Residential Use).

Source: Ord. 000406-81; Ord. 031211-11.
